  <brief_title>Platelet Response During the Second Cycle of Decitabine Can Predict Response and Survival for Myelodysplastic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retrospective Study for Predictive Marker for Decitabine Treament in MDS Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
